CHG26003.text:
CHG26003                   17/6/75
CHANGE PROPOSAL    : PROVIDE A MEANS TO PERMIT A 'ONCE ONLY'
        OVER-RIDE TO A DATASET FOR KEYWORDS LIKE BUFFNO,OPTCD ETC.
        THIS SEEMS MOST LOGICAL AT THE PROGRAM DECLARE LEVEL.
        E.G.  DCL X DS SYS1.DATASET;
              DCL Y PROG A READS X BUFFNO 10 OPTCD C B READS B;
              DCL Z PROG A READS X BUFFNO 1;
SUMMARY:PROVIDE A TEMPORARY OVERRIDE MECHANISM.
OVERRIDES CHANGE.

